{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_12","type":"agent_message","text":"The actual breakage is narrower than a general missing-reflection case: native runtime can construct the renderer in one path, but the fallback path cannot read `org/apache/log4j/EnhancedThrowableRenderer.class` as a resource from the renderer’s class loader. I’m inspecting the existing metadata around that class and then I’ll add the minimal entry needed for the class-resource lookup."}}
